<component type="desktop">
  <id>net.bugabinga.eos.FileIntegrity</id>
  <metadata_license>GPL3</metadata_license>
  <name>File Integrity Checker</name>
  <summary>Validate integrity of your files.</summary>
  <description>
        <p>Integrated file integrity validation for Elementary OS. This application provides a glance at all relevant means of validation of any file you wish.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>checksums</li>
      <li>PGP</li>
    </ul>
     <p>Furthermore, the context-menu of the <em>Files</em> manager is extended to enable generation and validation of checksums.</p>
    <p>Last but not least, files in your <b>~/Downloads</b> folder are automatically validated if an appropriate companion file is found.
    Typically, providers of larger file downloads also provide a download of an additional file, containing some means of validation. Typically checksums or sometimes a PGP key.</p>
    <p>Simply download these files additionally into your <b>~/Downloads</b> folder and the <em>File Integrity Checker</em> will show the validation result in your <em>Files</em> manager.</p>
  </description>
  <custom>
     <value key="x-appcenter-color-primary">rgb(162,46,55)</value>
     <value key="x-appcenter-color-primary-text">rgb(255, 255, 255)</value>
     <value key="x-appcenter-suggested-price">15</value>
  </custom>
</component>
